               <p>WILLIAM CLAYTON. I am a <rs id="t18301209-262-viclabel1474" type="occupation">carpenter</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301209-262-victim2185 t18301209-262-viclabel1474"></join>. I was in <placeName id="t18301209-262-crimeloc1475">Marylebone-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18301209-262-crimeloc1475" type="placeName" value="Marylebone-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18301209-262-crimeloc1475" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301209-262-off1472 t18301209-262-crimeloc1475"></join> on the 10th of December, at half-past eight o'clock - Harris spoke to me; I then felt and missed my handkerchief - I saw the prisoner, and took him; he dropped it, but I did not see him - I saw it first behind him: this is it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18301209-262-person2186">
                  GEORGE 
                  HARRIS
               <interp inst="t18301209-262-person2186" type="surname" value="HARRIS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18301209-262-person2186" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18301209-262-person2186" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an upholsterer. I was in Marylebone-street - I saw the prosecutor there; the prisoner and another person went up to him - the prisoner took up his coat with one hand, and took out his handkerchief - I told the gentleman, and he went back with me to the prisoner, who stood in the road: I said, "That is the one who picked your pocket;" I had seen him put the handkerchief into his outside pocket - Mr. Clayton took hold of him; he took him along, and I saw the prisoner put his hand into his pocket, take out the handkerchief, and throw it into a passage; I gave it to the Policeman.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18301209-262-person2187">
                  GEORGE 
                  STONE
               <interp inst="t18301209-262-person2187" type="surname" value="STONE"></interp>
